125
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:27,960
Master.

126
00:06:30,420 --> 00:06:30,860
Go.

127
00:06:32,220 --> 00:06:35,090
Ask someone to clean her up

128
00:06:35,140 --> 00:06:36,870
and give her some good clothes.

129
00:06:36,909 --> 00:06:38,370
