221
00:10:21,270 --> 00:10:23,670
Well, after suffering comes happiness...

222
00:10:28,870 --> 00:10:30,400
Like I'd be waiting for you!

223
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,360
Okay, this is it.

224
00:10:46,590 --> 00:10:47,320
What is this?

225
00:10:47,530 --> 00:10:48,650
It calms the nerves.

226
00:10:48,650 --> 00:10:49,830
It can help this old man

227
00:10:49,830 --> 00:10:51,030
fall into deep sleep.

228
00:11:34,010 --> 00:11:35,210
What took you so long?

229
00:11:35,390 --> 00:11:37,090
I've already drunk 800 rounds.

230
00:11:37,090 --> 00:11:38,220
