232
00:11:39,830 --> 00:11:40,890
Let's hurry and go.

233
00:11:46,020 --> 00:11:46,680
Who's that?

234
00:11:51,460 --> 00:11:53,060
I can't take it anymore, sir.

235
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:55,750
I can't drink anymore. I have to go back.

236
00:12:38,830 --> 00:12:39,310
Hurry.

237
00:12:40,300 --> 00:12:41,030
Miss Man'er.

238
00:12:41,650 --> 00:12:42,770
