241
00:12:45,470 --> 00:12:46,200
That's good.

242
00:12:46,330 --> 00:12:46,930
Thirteen.

243
00:12:50,230 --> 00:12:51,860
Yes, this is it.

244
00:12:52,420 --> 00:12:53,050
Three.

245
00:12:53,660 --> 00:12:54,520
This is for you.

246
00:12:54,850 --> 00:12:55,710
As for the rest,

247
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:56,990
