248
00:12:56,990 --> 00:12:57,590
Don't worry.

249
00:12:57,590 --> 00:12:58,110
Okay.

250
00:12:59,150 --> 00:13:00,500
Man'er, it's getting late.

251
00:13:00,500 --> 00:13:01,520
Let's go home now.

252
00:13:01,860 --> 00:13:02,760
